default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultEnergy savings from cavity wall insulation are
default 
defaultgreater than those from loft and solid wall
default 
defaultinsulation, due to the combination of uptake
default 
defaultnumbers and the amount
default each installation can
default 
defaultsave. The cavity wall insulation savings account for
default 
defaultmore than the other two measures added together
default 
defaultby 2020. Solid wall insulation has the greatest
default 
defaultvariability as there remains
default 
