defaultBy extending the sch
defaulteme to include gas heat pumps as they come to the market, it would increase the appeal to ‘on gas grid’ customers and expand the potential reduction in carbon emissions without the need to build upstream infrastructure.
default 
defaultDeploying energy efficiency measures
default including insulation will be a vital first step in helping to reduce heat used in homes and buildings. The Government’s Green Deal programme will provide support for individuals and businesses making energy efficiency improvements to their homes and build
defaultings.
