defaultWe welcome support for domestic low carbon technologies proposed under the RHI, however ask that policy makers ensure sufficient scope and flexibility – either now or when commercially available – in funding support for technologies which will be im
defaultportant in utilising natural gas more efficiently, 
defaulte.g.
default dual fuel appliances and gas heat pumps. 
